  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AccountData
    AccountData is a class that extends JPanel and is used to create and display a field for entering account data, such as username, password, and security question.
    ApartmentData
    A panel that contain all apartment data The data are displayed 2 in a row and for the water contors the consum is also shown
    ApInfoPanel
    Panel for showing apartment information.
    CheckCreatedDocL
    A listener class that implements the DocumentListener interface and is used to check if a document has been updated by changing the content color.
    ContorLine
    A JPanel class that displays a title and three AccountData objects representing old and new meter readings, and optionally consumption.
    MessagePanel
    A costum panel to display message it has rounded borders and a stroke in the left or right side
    PanelRound
    A customized JPanel with rounded corners and drop shadow effect.
    PayStatusUpdate
    PayStatusUpdate is a custom JPanel used to display and update the payment status of all apartments from an association.
    PSUpdate
    The PSUpdate class represents a graphical user interface for updating the payment status of an apartment.
    RoundedBorder
    A round border that can have a stroke on the left or right
    TablePanel
